title: Sally's Salon - Beauty Secrets Platinum Edition
description: Treat yourself to Sally's Salon - Beauty Secrets Platinum Edition and catch up with your favorite beautician. She and her new sidekick François are making the town a little more beautiful, one treatment at a time - but when Sally's favorite singer Julio plans to visit the town, she finds herself caught up in a romantic adventure. See what happens in Sally's Salon - Beauty Secrets Platinum Edition
